TOPVISION DISPLA said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 67.78% to NT$26,615,000 from NT$82,597,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2011           4/2010
Sales             26,615           82,597    
YOY%             -67.78%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            122,554          883,251    
YOY%             -86.12% 
=================================================================
 